
  Makuhita    Fighting Type Pokémon

  MAKUHITA is tenacious - it will 
  keep getting up and attacking 
  its foe however many times it 
  is knocked down.  Every time 
  it gets back up, Makuhita 
  stores more energy in its body 
  for evolving. 
	Evolution Chain
      Makuhita ► Hariyama

